** MSG
E-01 INPUT SUPPLIER CODE.
E-02 INPUT SUPPLIER FACTRY CODE.
E-03 INPUT WIRE.
E-04 INPUT WIRE DIAMETER.
E-05 INPUT PARTS CODE.
E-06 THIS DATA IS NOT IN WIRE KANBAN MASTER FILE.
E-07 THIS DATA IS NOT IN ROD KANBAN MASTER FILE.
E-08 THIS PAGE IS DISPLAYED THE DATA OF TOP PAGE.
E-09 THIS PAGE IS DISPLAYED THR DATA OF BOTTOM PAGE.
E-10 INPUT DATA IS NOT CORRECT.
E-11 INPUT UNIT PRICE CODE. ( 'YEN' OR 'US\')
E-12 INPUT UNIT PRICE.
E-13 INPUT UNIT.
E-14 INPUT BEGINNING DATE.
E-15 INPUT END DATE.
E-16 END DATE IS PAST DATE OF BEGINNING DATE.
E-17 NO DATA CAN BE ADDED BY THE EXISTED DATA.
E-18 DATE OF YEAR IS PAST TO 2000.
E-19 DATE OF MONTH IS DIFFERENT.
E-20 DATE OF DAY IS DIFFERENT.
E-21 THIS SUPPLIER CODE IS NOT DETAIL MASTER FILE.
E-22 THE UNIT OF PRICE IS 'K'. ( K = KG )
